<HEADLINE>
NEGOTIATORS DITHER; KOSOVARS SHIVER    
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors)   (This 400-word ``separate buy'' commentary is from the
International Herald Tribune.)  
  
