   TRAVEL
</P>
<P>
   COXNET TRAVEL 0330-ONLINE TRAVEL _ Finding that rock-bottom
airfare on-line is easier said than done, but that doesn't mean
it's impossible. Deal seekers willing to do more work for the
elusive cheap ticket can visit dozens of Web sites. (Bischoff,
Dayton Daily News) Art includes 4-column color illustration of
plane emerging from a computer.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: MILLENIUM CRUISE _ More than 60 people from Palm Beach
County, Fla., are going on a cruise to seven continents, 27
countries, 34 ports. They'll leave Athens, Greece, Nov. 20, 1999,
on the small Ocean Explorer I and return to Athens March 25, 2000.
Along the way, they will celebrate the millennium in style.
(Blackerby, Palm Beach Post)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: TRAVEL BRIEFS _ During the Easter season, children
visiting New England have a choice of several historical sites for
egg hunting. (Staff, N.Y. Times News Service)
</P>
