a best selling semi-mystery novel every year, is something of a
phenomenon in more ways than one. In this time of almost anything
goes in the way of sex and violence in our entertainment media
forms, Grisham's stories never delve into either, but still sell
like the proverbial hotcakes. (Milner, Lufkin Daily News) MOVED
</P>
