<P>
   ROLLERDERBY _ Roller Derby is back, with more than a dollop of
sex appeal, and a healthy borrowing from pro wrasslin'. The
Nashville Network's ``Roller Jam'' has co-ed teams (gals vs. gals,
guys vs. guys), tighter costumes, tattoos, cleavage, obnoxious
fans, fights, and a growing audience of teen-age boys, among
others. We talk to two skaters, one a 20-year-old Atlanta woman
who's on leave from UGA to be a Roller Jammer and look at the Jerry
Springer-ization of inline skating. Kloer, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 28. WITH PHOTOS. MOVED
</P>
