<TEXT>
<P>
   Sports stories from The New York Times News Service for Friday,
March 26.
</P>
<P>
   BKW-ARATON-COLUMN (San Jose, Calif.) _ Sports of the Times on
NCAA women's Final Four, to be played Friday night. By Harvey
Araton.
