Knick who is now the leading scorer for Golden State. The Knicks
will not play the Warriors this season, so they will not get a
chance to catch up with the player who was such a key part of their
1990s battles. By Mike Wise.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-METS-PITCHING (Port St. Lucie, Fla.) _ Suddenly, there is
intrigue in the Mets' camp, with Hideo Nomo being sent to the
minors as a possible prelude to being cut outright, with the Mets
purusing 40-year-old Orel Hershiser, and with Manager Bobby
Valentine and General Manager Steve Phillips possibly disagreeing
about how to proceed with a starting rotation that doesn't look all
that formidable right now. By Jason Diamos.
