<BODY>
 AM-ADD-NYT-BUDGET  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Add N.Y. Times News Service budget for papers of Friday, March
26.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; ENTERTAINMENT  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   CORIGLIANO (Undated) _ Composer John Corigliano's long-awaited
``Dylan Thomas Trilogy'' is to have its premiere. By Allan Kozinn.
With photo.
</P>
<P>
   CLOSER-THEATER-REVIEW (New York) _ Ben Brantley reviews Patrick
