</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    FINALLY, THE B-2 GOES INTO COMBAT
 &HT;    With KOSOVO-B2-0326.
 &HT;    By BOB DEANS 
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service 
<TEXT>
<P>
   B-2 SPIRIT
