<HEADER>
A4238 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-KOSOVO-MILO     03-25 0033
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-KOSOVO-MILOSEVIC-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-MILOSEVIC (Belgrade) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, March. 25.
</P>
</TEXT>
