Speaker Dennis Hastert, right, greets a tourist outside the Capitol
en route to a press conference on Thursday. The House was expected
to pass the Republican budget plan, driving toward a big tax cut
and a showdown later this year with the Clinton Administration over
the nation's priorities in an anticipated era of fiscal plenty.
(Shana Raab/New York Times Photo)
</P>
