<DOCNO> NYT19990325.0391 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-25 22:22 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4504 &Cx1f; taf-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-EDIT-KOSOVO-NYT &LR;      03-25 0479
